Interface SAMUNotificationImplI

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SAMUNotificationCI
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SAMUNotificationImplI
    The interface SAMUNotificationImplI declares the notifications that can be sent by a SAMU station.
